data.description: A LOWER INTEREST RATE IN 2024?? IT'S POSSIBLE WITH THIS HOUSE! SELLER OFFERING $5,000 CREDIT TO BUYER FOR CLOSING COSTS, RATE BUYDOWNS, ETC! This is a gorgeous contemporary home in the Mustang school district with 4 bedrooms, 2 1/2 baths and a 3 car garage. With great curb appeal on a quiet street, there is so much to love about this home! One of the sellers favorite parts is the backyard. It backs to a greenbelt area with cows behind, which they love to watch from their back patio. In fact, they added an electric screen to the patio so they can enjoy it year-round! The inside of the home is beautiful with modern style and finishings. The star of the show is the huge kitchen with a big island, walk-in pantry, coffee bar, gas range, stainless apron sink, under-cabinet lighting and other custom features! There is a nice mud hall bench in the laundry room, hidden behind a pretty wood barn door from the kitchen. The living room is inviting with a high, vaulted ceiling, wood beam, a gas fireplace, and surround sound speakers. The 4 bedrooms are split with 2 on each side of the home. The master has a stunning bathroom with a freestanding tub, 2 vanities, a large tiled shower, and a fantastic walk-in closet with built-in dressers. Other notable amenities include Cat 5 wiring, a security system, and a sprinkler system. The home also has a Shluter Kerdi waterproof shower system, tankless water heater, and LED-lit mirrors.
